# Optional. A single RPC endpoint used for BOTH mainnet and devnet.
# Must be Photon-capable (Helius / Triton) — the Lookup/Verify pages read
# compressed PDAs, and the public api.mainnet-beta.solana.com fallback will
# NOT work for those reads. When unset, each cluster uses a public default.
#
# VITE_CC_VRF_RPC_URL=https://your-helius-or-triton-rpc/?api-key=YOUR_KEY
